hazmat:HazmatCodeSimpleType

simpleType HazmatCodeSimpleType in namespace http://release.niem.gov/niem/codes/hazmat/5.0/

Definition

A data type for a United Nations/North American (UN/NA) Hazardous Materials Code pertaining to a hazardous material.
